Text: FW prebonene dinnerHpst From Donald Tencellent Jr Sent Wednesday May PM To Cc Donald Tencellent Jr Subject prebonene dinner hi guysi know that over the past few weeks i have been asking you guys if you could come out to a prebonene dinner on next thursday may st at a site tbdthe day is about a week away now and i hope that we can all still hang outim emailing you guys to see who is still in or if there are any flakes as the date grows closeradditionallywhere would you guys like to goany place new in houston that we need to check out just let me know so i can make the plans and if i left anybody out who wants to go sneal griggs martin huntman frank the more the better as far as im concernedthanks donny
